<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Let their table before them become a snare;</para>

<para style="q1">when they think they are in safety, let it become a trap.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="23" style="v" />Let their eyes be darkened so that they cannot see;</para>

<para style="q1">and always make their loins shake.</para>
